aves.dpt.impl.ctrl

Class AvesManagerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • aves.dpt.impl.ctrl.AvesManagerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AvesEventManager, AvesManager, java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class AvesManagerImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements AvesManager, AvesEventManager, java.awt.event.KeyListener
    This class implements a AvesManager. It organizes requests for AvesObjects from the Factory and delegates the display of these AvesObjects to the AvesViewer. It receives user input as a callback from the AvesViewer and analyzes this input to make further decisions.
    Author:
    svlieffe 2012/03/29
